params.description:
A deeply nest associative array, which allows
                         you to bind other Controllers and Models to the
                         Offer Model.
                         (Eg., ['Affiliate' => [
                                  'filters' => [
                                     'Affiliate.company' => ['xyz']
                                     ],
                                  'fields' => [
                                     'Affiliate.id',
                                     'Affiliate.company'
                                     ]
                                  ]
                               ])
